225
00:12:06.830 --> 00:12:08.658
Connecticut is not in Beverly Hills.

226
00:12:08.701 --> 00:12:11.661
Everybody wants a taste of
Beverly Hills, even in Connecticut.


227
00:12:11.704 --> 00:12:14.446
Especially in Connecticut, believe me.

228
00:12:14.489 --> 00:12:16.056
You want people coming to your mall,

229
00:12:16.100 --> 00:12:17.797
not just because they can buy things here

230
00:12:17.841 --> 00:12:19.136
that you get cheaper somewhere else.

231
00:12:19.146 --> 00:12:22.323
You want them to have an experience.

232
00:12:24.935 --> 00:12:26.458
You know what I mean.

233
00:12:30.114 --> 00:12:31.463
You didn't stand a chance, kid.

234
00:12:35.510 --> 00:12:37.599
Thanks.
Excuse me for breathing.


235
00:12:37.643 --> 00:12:39.732
Nothing personal.

236
00:12:39.776 --> 00:12:42.256
You had vision, talked a
kind of poetry. It scared them.


237
00:12:42.300 --> 00:12:45.085
These guys wear suspenders and belts.

238
00:12:45.129 --> 00:12:46.903
I should've told them
what they wanted to hear,


239
00:12:46.913 --> 00:12:49.046
Give less than I got,

240
00:12:49.089 --> 00:12:51.831
but I can't give less than
I got. I don't know how.


241
00:12:51.875 --> 00:12:54.616
My name is Max Sherman.
Let me buy you a drink.


242
00:12:58.142 --> 00:12:59.491
Thank you.

243
00:12:59.534 --> 00:13:00.579
Cheers.

244
00:13:03.756 --> 00:13:05.802
Got family?

245
00:13:05.845 --> 00:13:07.325
Uh, a wife.

246
00:13:07.368 --> 00:13:08.882
We haven't had time to have children yet.

247
00:13:08.892 --> 00:13:10.371
Yeah, me neither.

248
00:13:12.373 --> 00:13:14.027
So, where are you from?

249
00:13:14.071 --> 00:13:17.944
I got a couple things out
here, some stuff in Texas.


250
00:13:17.988 --> 00:13:20.512
My major operation is
California, Southern California.


251
00:13:20.555 --> 00:13:21.948
You live out there?

252
00:13:21.992 --> 00:13:23.471
I live where the money is.

